OL,3,CCouncils call for urgent shake-up in
OL,4,Cthe 'outdated' way London is run
OL,6,FLeaders of London's 32 boroughs say
OL,7,Fthe way London is run needs an 'urgent
OL,8,Fupdate', adding the current system was
OL,9,Fdesigned in a different century, for a
OL,10,Fdifferent era.
OL,12,FThe boroughs have no formal decision-
OL,13,Fmaking role within the Greater London
OL,14,FAuthority at City Hall, in stark
OL,15,Fcontrast to authorities in Greater
OL,16,FManchester and the West Midlands.
