OL,3,CCouncils call for urgent shake-up in
OL,4,Cthe 'outdated' way London is run
OL,6,FThe collective body which represents
OL,7,Feach borough wants a new Combined
OL,8,FBoard ` made up of the Mayor of London
OL,9,Fand a London Councils' Executive
OL,10,FCommittee.
OL,12,FCouncils claim the changes would bring
OL,13,FLondon in line with other devolution
OL,14,Fdeals and enable quicker and more
OL,15,Feffective decision-making, as well as
OL,16,Fimproving outcomes for Londoners and
OL,17,Fensuring better value for money.
