OL,3,CCouncils call for urgent shake-up in
OL,4,Cthe 'outdated' way London is run
OL,6,F"The prospect of more devolved powers
OL,7,Fand funding to the capital is an
OL,8,Fexciting one ` but we must ensure
OL,9,FLondon's devolution settlement works
OL,10,Fas effectively and efficiently as
OL,11,Fpossible," said Cllr Claire Holland,
OL,12,FChair of London Councils.
OL,14,F"Giving boroughs a seat at the table
OL,15,Fand a proper say in regional decision-
OL,16,Fmaking will put us in a far stronger
OL,17,Fposition to tackle the challenges we
OL,18,Fface as a city and drive growth in
OL,19,FLondon.
