OL,3,CCouncils call for urgent shake-up in
OL,4,Cthe 'outdated' way London is run
OL,6,F"We have worked hard to build cross-
OL,7,Fparty consensus across the 32 boroughs
OL,8,Ffor a pragmatic solution that enables
OL,9,Fjoint decision-making.
OL,11,F"We must seize this opportunity to
OL,12,Fhardwire collaboration between the
OL,13,FMayor and boroughs into our devolution
OL,14,Fdeal so that we can all deliver better
OL,15,Foutcomes for Londoners," she added.
OL,17,FThe Mayor of London sets the budget
OL,18,Fand is responsible for making London a
OL,19,Fbetter place for everyone who visits,
OL,20,Flives or works in the city. The Mayor
OL,21,Fis elected every four years.
