OL,3,CCouncils call for urgent shake-up in
OL,4,Cthe 'outdated' way London is run
OL,6,FLondon currently relies on voluntary
OL,7,Fcollaboration between the Mayor and
OL,8,Fboroughs. London Councils says a lack
OL,9,Fof formal arrangements and need to
OL,10,Fnegotiate on a case-by-case basis
OL,11,Fslows down decision-making and limits
OL,12,Fthe ability to make the best use of
OL,13,Fcollective resources.
OL,15,FThe government is preparing to publish
OL,16,Fits English Devolution Bill and has
OL,17,Fsignalled more devolution could come
OL,18,Fto London.
