OL,3,CCouncils call for urgent shake-up in
OL,4,Cthe 'outdated' way London is run
OL,6,FPart of a joint statement from each
OL,7,FLondon borough said: "We want London
OL,8,Fto continue to succeed as a global
OL,9,Fcapital city and having a Mayor who is
OL,10,Fempowered to advocate for London on
OL,11,Fthe national and international stage
OL,12,Fis a vital part of that ` but we
OL,13,Fcannot let boroughs be left behind.
OL,15,F"If we do, we will limit our city's
OL,16,Fability to drive the inclusive
OL,17,Feconomic growth and positive change
OL,18,Fthat we all want to see.
